<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-818] Should preserve the exchange type in the routing slip</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-818</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently, the routing slip will create a new InOut exchange for each target based on the target endpoint type. This means that someone calling from a jbi endpoint (or other endpoint with custom exchange) into the routing slip will have their exchange type changed (to mostly likely DefaultExchange). I will be including a patch to fix this issue shortly. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
